lead_paragraph: Atlantic City arrested 24 people who blocked streets in the New Jersey city on Wednesday as hundreds of casino workers demonstrated against plans by the Trump Taj Mahal to cut pension and health benefits.

headline.main: Atlantic City Casino Workers Block Streets to Protest Cuts
